cscribe
=======

A simple command line / tui program to assist in transcribing music.

This is still in development.


Features:
---------

- Jumping and seeking
- Marking and replaying
- Vim keybindings


Planned features:
-----------------

- Tempo adjustments (retaining pitch)


Notes
-----

mp3 is currently not supported.


Dependencies
------------

- libsndfile
- ncurses
- portaudio


Resources / Thanks
------------------

PortAudio / libsndfile help:
http://music.columbia.edu/pipermail/portaudio/2004-December/004064.html
